[Intro]
1:54 Start: "Hi~Hello Everyone.. It‚Äôs me Gawr Gura form hololive english myth"
2:16 "Thank you for coming tonight. And for.. Being here. It really means a lot to me that you‚Äôre here right now."

‚îó3:25 -Gura will Leave hololive on May 1 2025 JST
 ‚îó"My reasons beeing "Disagreements with management and company direction" 

[Gura's Journey]
3:44 "I debuted in September of 2020 with 4 other incredibly talented girls I respect and admire..."
‚îó3:57 "I had barely any streaming or singing-dancing Experience before joining this company..."
4:07 Gura's struggles: "It was.. incredibly exciting but also very intense and unexpected to be suddenly surrounded by so many eyes and expectations..."
‚î£4:19 "I remember there being many days where the stress was so overwhelming I couldn't eat or keep food down..."
‚î£4:30 "But the continuous support and patience of my wonderful community helped to lessen that feeling...."
‚îó4:39 "And Pushed me to go on to do things that I didn't even know i was capable of."

[Gura's Thanks] 
4:45 "I am so lucky and so thankful for each and every one of you.."
‚îó4:54 "For the opportunities given to me.. And the Almost 5 Years we've been able to spend together"
5:05 "I love singing for you, and performing for you on stage or form my bedroom.." 
5:11 "You helped pull me out of my shell and I went from being too scared to sing alone in my shower to singing live Infront of hundreds of thousands of people" 
5:24 "When I think about how many of you I've been able to connect with.. It brings me so much joy"
‚î£5:36 "It‚Äôs been an Honour and a dream come true to be your shark. Your Gooba."
‚î£ 5:44 "With You.. I've been able to achieve what I thought for a very long time was impossible for a girl like me.
‚îó5:53 "To feel a part of something.. and to belong."

[Gura's Love for the Community]
6:01  I love being an Idol, and Vtubing and watching all of my senpai, kouhai, and the entire Vtubing community grow into a successful world  
‚î£6:17 "I love the banter We‚Äôve shared over the years your clips, Compilations, cosplays, fanart. Every single bit of it"
‚îó6:30 "I am so lucky to have been loved in such a way‚Ä¶ "
6:35 Gura has Everyone's letters:  "I will seal them and keep them forever until the archaeologist try and dig them up in 300 years  and try to decipher what a Gawr Gura was"

[Closing Thanks]
6:57 "Thank you for your compassion, your creativity, an your dedication to me.." 
‚î£7:06 "Thank you for waiting for me to return, when the outside world becomes too much. Let's have as much fun as we can together during these last 2 weeks."
‚îó7:30 "And while my time hear may be coming to and end... I will cherish the memories we‚Äôve made together forever"
7:39 - Gura has one final Project...
7:47 "I'm feeling really Optimistic for the future and I hope you are too. Thank you everyone for letting me be your little shark."

Thank you for everything Gura. o7

Thanks again for a great stream. Filling in some gaps of words and mind silently untold.

Keep doing your happy themed stream and content. Be strong because we are here for you.
